<div class="container mt-4 mb-5">
  <h2 class="mt-4 mb-3">
        Frequently Asked Questions
  </h2>
  <div id="exampleAccordion" data-children=".item">
    <div class="item">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#exampleAccordion" href="#exampleAccordion1" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="exampleAccordion1">
        What is SmartRoof?
      </a>
      <div id="exampleAccordion1" class="collapse show" role="tabpanel">
        <p class="mb-3">
          SmartRoof is an online roofing marketplace. We utilize satellite imaging technology to measure your roof and provide you with an instant, free quote. We then connect you to local trusted installers who can professionally take care of your roofing needs and help deal with insurance.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#exampleAccordion" href="#exampleAccordion2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleAccordion2">
        Which areas do you serve?
      </a>
      <div id="exampleAccordion2" class="collapse" role="tabpanel">
        <p class="mb-3">
          Every state and major city in the United States.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#exampleAccordion" href="#exampleAccordion3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleAccordion3">
        Is the quote generated by the online estimator tool final?
      </a>
      <div id="exampleAccordion3" class="collapse" role="tabpanel">
        <p class="mb-3">
          No, our online estimation tool provides you with a fair estimate as to how much your roof will cost to replace. After your “Onsite Inspection” you will receive a final, detailed quote from us via email. You can get quotes from multiple installers if you’d like.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#exampleAccordion" href="#exampleAccordion4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleAccordion4">
       What is an “Onsite Inspection”?
      </a>
      <div id="exampleAccordion4" class="collapse" role="tabpanel">
        <p class="mb-3">
         Once you request an “Onsite Inspection”, SmartRoof will send out an installer to your property to inspect the roof, address any issues, answer any questions, and ultimately help choose the right roofing system for you.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#exampleAccordion" href="#exampleAccordion5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleAccordion5">
        Do SmartRoof installers have insurance coverage?
      </a>
      <div id="exampleAccordion5" class="collapse" role="tabpanel">
        <p class="mb-3">
          We service every state and major city in the United States.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#exampleAccordion" href="#exampleAccordion6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleAccordion6">
        Do SmartRoof installers have insurance coverage?
      </a>
      <div id="exampleAccordion6" class="collapse" role="tabpanel">
        <p class="mb-3">
          All of our installers have WSIB coverage and liability insurance. SmartRoof carries full liability insurance as well.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#exampleAccordion" href="#exampleAccordion7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleAccordion7">
       Does SmartRoof do the installation?
      </a>
      <div id="exampleAccordion7" class="collapse" role="tabpanel">
        <p class="mb-3">
         No, SmartRoof does not complete the roof installation. Our job is to provide you with the best roof installers in your area to complete the work at a fair price. An installer must pass through rigorous screening to be eligible to serve homeowners on our platform.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#exampleAccordion" href="#exampleAccordion8" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleAccordion8">
        Who do I pay?
      </a>
      <div id="exampleAccordion8" class="collapse" role="tabpanel">
        <p class="mb-3">
          Once the work is complete and you’re happy, you pay the installers. Our service is free to use for homeowners.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#exampleAccordion" href="#exampleAccordion9" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleAccordion9">
       How do I pay?
      </a>
      <div id="exampleAccordion9" class="collapse" role="tabpanel">
        <p class="mb-3">
         Our installers accept checks, money orders, or cash.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#exampleAccordion" href="#exampleAccordion10" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleAccordion10">
        Does my roof come with a warranty?
      </a>
      <div id="exampleAccordion10" class="collapse" role="tabpanel">
        <p class="mb-3">
        Once the job is complete and full payment is made to the installer, SmartRoof will provide you with all your warranty documentation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="item">
      <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#exampleAccordion" href="#exampleAccordion11" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="exampleAccordion11">
       How can I get in touch with SmartRoof?
      </a>
      <div id="exampleAccordion11" class="collapse" role="tabpanel">
        <p class="mb-3">
         Give us a call at +1 (678) 439-6456 and talk directly to one of our customer service agents. Or email us at hello@smartroof.io
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
